	<h2> Menu: Pork Tapa </h2>
	<h3> Ingredients: </h3>
		<ul class="unorderedList">
			<li>0.5 kg of pork shoulder</li>
			<li>1 sachet of magic sarap</li>
			<li>2 tbsp of soy sauce</li>
			<li>0.25 tsp of ground pepper</li>
			<li>4 cloves of garlic</li>
			<li>2 tbsp of brown sugar</li>
			<li>1pc of hot chili peppers</li>
			<li>2 tbsp of vegetable oil</li>
			<li>0.25 cup of spiced sugar</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="container">
	<h3> Method: </h3>
		<ol class="orderedList">
			<li>Step 1 - Marinate with magic sarap,soy sauce,pepper garlic,sugar and chili. Refrigate overnight. </li>
			<li>Step 2 - Remove pork tapa from the refrigerator 1 hour before cooking. </li>
			<li>Step 3 - Saut√© marinated pork in oil. Cook until golden brown. Transfer on a searing plate and serve with spiced vinegar.</li>
		</ol>
